[
    {
        "content": "<p>Do you think the <a href=\"https://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/products/sku/191792/intel-core-i79700-processor-12m-cache-up-to-4-70-ghz/specifications.html\">Intel Core i7-9700 processor</a> will remain powerful enough for building and testing Lean projects? I've used it for five years, and I'm planning to upgrade it in two or three years.</p>",
        "id": 564933308,
        "sender_full_name": "Bulhwi Cha",
        "timestamp": 1766376503
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Your current CPU's 3.0GHz base frequency is good enough. If you often build super large projects (like mathlib) from scratch, you might need more cores/threads, but for most purposes 8 threads is enough.</p>",
        "id": 565038188,
        "sender_full_name": "Gavin Zhao",
        "timestamp": 1766421703
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I've found that RAM size is much more important to me than my CPU. You're much more likely to be limited by Lean files that take up several GB of RAM each when opened. You should monitor your RAM usage to see the files that you typically open and check if you need to upgrade the RAM.</p>",
        "id": 565038204,
        "sender_full_name": "Gavin Zhao",
        "timestamp": 1766421710
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>(my usecase requires me to have multiple files opened side-by-side, and each file I open in Lean InfoView sits there in RAM even after I close the file in my editor unless, uh, I don't even know how to tell the Lean LSP to drop it)</p>",
        "id": 565038371,
        "sender_full_name": "Gavin Zhao",
        "timestamp": 1766421782
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>One of my Lean files imports <code>Mathlib.Data.Set.Basic</code> and contains two theorems I wrote. It takes up 861 MiB of RAM. Can someone explain the reason for this? I'm just curious.</p>\n<div class=\"spoiler-block\"><div class=\"spoiler-header\">\n<p>My Lean file</p>\n</div><div class=\"spoiler-content\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\">-- this code is written in Lean v4.26.0</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">module</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">public</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Data</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Basic</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">namespace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Function</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">universe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ext'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Surjective</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">haB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">haB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hsur</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">heq</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">ext</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hfx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">heq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hyB</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hfa₁</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hsur</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hyB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hfa₂</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">heq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">refine</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Subtype</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mk</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">inj</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">show</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hyB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">from</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">?_</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hfa₁</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hfa₂</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">subst</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ext_iff'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↔</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Surjective</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">exists</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↦</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">▸</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">property</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">exists</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">symm</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">▸</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">property</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">exists</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">▸</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">property</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ext'</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</div></div>",
        "id": 565109749,
        "sender_full_name": "Bulhwi Cha",
        "timestamp": 1766475070
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Data point: in October, I learned that 8 GB of RAM were not enough to reliably do <code>import Mathlib</code> in a project depending on mathlib without making your computer run out of memory. The module system and other fixes have helped somewhat (resp. will, if your project also uses the module system) --- but I wouldn't base my RAM choices on this. Go for at least 16GB of RAM, and even better 32 if you easily can.</p>",
        "id": 565122912,
        "sender_full_name": "Michael Rothgang",
        "timestamp": 1766481551
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"417769\">Bulhwi Cha</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113488-general/topic/desktop.20processors.20for.20using.20lean.20and.20other.20proof.20assistants/near/565109749\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>One of my Lean files imports <code>Mathlib.Data.Set.Basic</code> and contains two theorems I wrote. It takes up 861 MiB of RAM. Can someone explain the reason for this? I'm just curious.</p>\n<div class=\"spoiler-block\"><div class=\"spoiler-header\">\n<p>My Lean file</p>\n</div><div class=\"spoiler-content\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\">-- this code is written in Lean v4.26.0</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">module</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">public</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Data</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Basic</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">namespace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Function</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">universe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ext'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Surjective</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">haB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">haB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hsur</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">heq</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">ext</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hfx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">heq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hyB</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hfa₁</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hsur</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hyB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hfa₂</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">heq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">refine</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Subtype</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mk</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">inj</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">show</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hyB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">from</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">?_</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hfa₁</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hfa₂</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">subst</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxA</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ext_iff'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↔</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Surjective</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∧</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∃</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hxB</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">exists</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↦</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">▸</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">property</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">exists</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">⟨</span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">symm</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">▸</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">property</span><span class=\"bp\">⟩</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">exists</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">▸</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">property</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ext'</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Set</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p></div></div><br>\n</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>My guess is that Lean LSP has loaded <code>Prelude</code> + all the transitive imports of <code>Mathlib.Data.Set.Basic</code> into RAM...</p>",
        "id": 565189542,
        "sender_full_name": "Gavin Zhao",
        "timestamp": 1766510166
    },
    {
        "content": "<blockquote>\n<p>Go for at least 16GB of RAM, and even better 32 if you easily can.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>An unfortunate time to buy new RAM <span aria-label=\"sweat smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f605\" role=\"img\" title=\"sweat smile\">:sweat_smile:</span></p>",
        "id": 565189661,
        "sender_full_name": "Gavin Zhao",
        "timestamp": 1766510235
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I have a pair of 16 GB DDR4 RAM, and I guess I'll have to use it for the next few years. I was only able to upgrade my graphics card. <span aria-label=\"smiling face with tear\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f972\" role=\"img\" title=\"smiling face with tear\">:smiling_face_with_tear:</span></p>",
        "id": 565236836,
        "sender_full_name": "Bulhwi Cha",
        "timestamp": 1766546153
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Does Lean require more memory than other proof assistants like Rocq, Agda, Isabelle, and Metamath One?</p>",
        "id": 565247815,
        "sender_full_name": "Bulhwi Cha",
        "timestamp": 1766557437
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"766285\">Gavin Zhao</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113488-general/topic/desktop.20processors.20for.20using.20lean.20and.20other.20proof.20assistants/near/565038204\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I've found that RAM size is much more important to me than my CPU. You're much more likely to be limited by Lean files that take up several GB of RAM each when opened. You should monitor your RAM usage to see the files that you typically open and check if you need to upgrade the RAM.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Yes, but at a certain point, more RAM will not help, whereäs faster CPU will continuously help.</p>",
        "id": 565308210,
        "sender_full_name": "Martin Dvořák",
        "timestamp": 1766600980
    }
]